1. TITLE OF INVENTION

PI220 CRYSTAL BALL™ – Spherical Immersive Intelligence Environment for Real-Time Visualization, Digital Twin Interaction, Multi-Domain Monitoring, Engineering Design, Decision Support, and Predictive Analysis
https://i.ibb.co/HT3QNVb4/Prof-Dr-Jesse-Jessen.png
